  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink97-kilavi">puṟattoḻukkam iṉṟiyē irukkavum uḷateṉṟu pulanta talaimakaḷaip pulavi
          nīkkiya talaimakaṉ puṇarcciyatu iṟutikkaṇ taṉṉuḷḷē colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink97">
          <l>pakaṉṟai vāṉmalar miṭainta kōṭṭaik</l>
          <l>karuntā ḷerumaik kaṉṟu verūum</l>
          <l>poykai yūraṉ makaḷivaḷ</l>
          <l>poykaip pūviṉu naṟuntaṇ ṇiyaḷē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg xml:lang="en">

          <l> This is the girl (lit. daughter) of the man from a village with ponds</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the calf of the black-legged buffalo takes fright</l>
          <l rend="indent4"> from [his] horns piled high with white Jalap blossoms – </l>
          <l> she is cooler [and] more fragrant than the flowers in [that] pond.</l>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
